column4: is it me or does the kubuntu-desktop seem very unfinished compared to the gnome ubuntu-desktop?
what do u mean by unfinished?
a lot of ubuntu things are missing from the kde setup, I think. I haven't used it much because it bugs me that I cant find the things I have gotten used to in gnome.
but it might just be that I don't like kde anymore since I switched to gnome.
